Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:19.79,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,{\an8}Ghost Story: Eight Stories of Hachishaku\NPleasure Ahound
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:19.79,Hardsub,,0,0,10,,Heteromorphic Oddity\N"Hathishaku-sama. The Final Story Arc"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:36.55,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,We're almost at your destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:41.52,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know. Since were almost there, how about...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.43,0:00:46.98,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,we talk about something that you might fear the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:51.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,When it comes to nightmares, people\Nalways think "I'm so glad I woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:54.65,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad that wasn't real."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.65,0:00:59.24,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,But to actually think that, they need to\Nhave seen something, or so I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:05.08,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Once upon a time, there was a girl who was dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:07.46,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,In the dream, there was a train with a monkey that was
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:10.88,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,similar to something she'd seen at an\Namusement park when she was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:15.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Riding the train were several pale-faced people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:21.01,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,However, at some point, she was able\Nto figure out that it was all a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:28.48,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,She rode the train thinking, "I'll be fine\Nas long as I wake up from the dream."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:34.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,However the train kept moving forward,\Nnot even taking a moment to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.19,0:01:38.07,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,She wondered where exactly the train was\Nheading towards and thought that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:39.95,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,it was a very strange dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:45.37,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,But right when she started getting\Nrelaxed, an announcement played.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:50.08,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,The next stop is the gutting station. The gutting station.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:55.34,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,And then out of nowhere four figures appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:01:57.84,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,They went to the person furthest in the back and...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:01:59.26,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Slice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:04.97,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,And they cut her as if they were\Npreparing some kind of meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:10.36,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,One after another, the woman's organs\Nspewed out from within her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:15.36,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,The screams of being carved up accompanied with the\Nsordid smell of blood and flesh had her paralyzed with fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:36.59,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Disturbed by the grotesque sight before\Nher, she began to become distraught.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:39.22,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Doubts of whether or not this was really\Na dream or not flooded her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:42.01,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,She began fearing what might happen next.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:48.52,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,However despite her fear, she couldn't\Nwill herself to get off the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:50.77,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Clang. Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:53.31,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Clatter. Cling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:55.48,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,The train continued on its track, unperturbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:58.90,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,And then came the next announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:03.83,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Next is the carving station. Carving station.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:12.13,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,And then the things went to the person second\Nfrom the back and carved out her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:13.92,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Squish. Slurch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:15.38,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Gurgle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:16.96,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Splish splash.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:18.63,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Dabble dabble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:23.55,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,The woman trembled and her hairs stood up on end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:27.68,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,The simple reason being that the person next in line was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:29.23,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:37.07,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,"I need to wake up. I need to wake up!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:40.78,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,"This is a dream! This is just a bad dream!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:46.70,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,But the next announcement came and\Nit was even worse than the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:51.08,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Next up is the mincemeat stop. Mincemeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:53.88,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,"Wake up! Wake up! Wake up!! Wake up!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:55.67,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,"Hurry! Hurry up and wake up!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:57.21,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,"Wake up from this nightmare!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:07.35,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,And when she did wake up, she was in her usual room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:13.60,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,She was lying on her bed, covered in sweat and tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:17.15,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,"Oh, I'm so glad I woke up."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:19.48,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,"I'm so glad that wasn't real."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:24.11,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:28.70,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,The next stop is the end of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:34.96,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,And that's the last of my stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:38.25,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,That one was called "the monkey dream".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:43.17,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,No one knows where that girl is or how she's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:46.14,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,But here's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:52.06,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Dreams can only be called dreams\Nby people who can wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:58.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,If you can't wake up, then dreams are nothing\Nmore than reality at that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:05.78,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:08.03,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You don't look so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:09.91,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It's okay, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:16.42,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Your story just made me remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:21.67,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It made me remember the continuation to\Nthe Hachishaku-sama story from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:28.18,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,That kid began to be able to see dreams too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:33.43,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,A-kun, might have been attacked by Hachishaku-sama\Nand almost lost his life to her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:38.52,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,He was able to escape her grips with the help\Nof his grandfather and others from the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:41.90,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,And then he lived a peaceful life\Nas if nothing had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:44.24,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,With his usual friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:47.49,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Everything was supposed to have gone back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:25.07,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,But from that day on, she'd always appear in his dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:28.65,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,That soft and comforting get frightening touch...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:55.93,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Please... don't leave me by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:08.03,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,When he'd wake up, for some reason, there'd\Nonly be her sweet scent left around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:13.70,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,And a new day that made it seem as if the\Nlast night had never happened began.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:18.04,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Those days continued day after day for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:21.67,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,The boy grew older and slowly became an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:17.56,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Hachishaku-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:20.47,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Hachishaku-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:28.77,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Your boobs are so soft and so warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:59.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Your dick is so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:15.49,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Let me eat you up down here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:37.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You're such a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:39.70,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You're really such a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:13.44,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:16.15,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting for you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:19.57,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting for you to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:33.79,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,"Why did I meet her that day?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:37.46,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,"Why did she choose me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:40.26,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,He couldn't think of a single reason why, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:44.76,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,There was one thing that he wondered about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:51.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Why did he run away from her in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:59.61,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It's possible that he was no longer able\Nto tell his dreams apart from reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:06.16,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,He'd see her everywhere he went, not\Nsure if she was real or an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:19.00,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,He began seeing every woman with\Nlong hair and a hat as her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:21.92,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,He began being unable to go out with friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:29.26,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,"I want to go back."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:32.69,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,His head began to be filled with that and that alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:39.57,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,And amidst all of that, he received\Na call from his grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:43.57,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,The statue that sealed Hachishaku-sama\Nwas destroyed by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:50.74,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,And so he rushed to the village knowing\Nthat he'd probably be killed either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:54.42,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,He was at his wits' ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:57.75,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,She was calling for him this entire time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:13:00.09,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,But I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:08.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Am I still dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:10.47,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Hachishaku-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:12.10,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Po.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:19.02,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
